<h2>Itching or burning, Pain or discomfort, Pain with urination and Vaginal dryness</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms itching or burning, pain or discomfort, pain with urination and vaginal dryness including Urinary tract infection (UTI), Lice, and Perimenopause.</p>
<p>There  are 12 conditions  associated with itching or burning, pain or discomfort, pain with urination and vaginal dryness. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
